L.
Though the matter caused not only to those who failed, but to <persName id="#their_friends">their friends</persName> and kin a certain degree of shame and depression and sorrow for many days, <persName id="#cato">Cato</persName> bore what had happened with so little concern, that after anointing himself in the Campus he exercised at ball, and again after dinner, according to his wont, he went down into the Forum without his shoes and tunic, and walked about with <persName id="#his_intimates">his intimates</persName>.
