LIV.
Being sent to <placeName id="#asia">Asia</placeName> to help those there who were collecting vessels and <persName id="#an_army">an army</persName>, he took with him <persName id="#his_sister">his sister</persName> <personGrp id="#servilia">Servilia</personGrp> and <persName id="#her_young_child">her young child</persName> by <personGrp id="#lucullus">Lucullus</personGrp>.
