LVI.
<persName id="#conjecturing">Conjecturing</persName> that <persName id="#pompeius_magnus">Pompeius Magnus</persName> would make his escape to <personGrp id="#egypt">Egypt</personGrp> or to <personGrp id="#libya">Libya</personGrp>, and being in haste to join him, <persName id="#cato">Cato</persName> with all whom he had about him weighed anchor and set sail after permitting all those to go away or stay behind who were not ready to accompany him.
